Package MyContacts

Class Summary
Contact This class creates object Contact and contains all methods that deals with this object. Object Contact represents a simple phone contact. Object Contact attributes : *Last name of the contact. *First name of the contact. *Address of the contact. *City of the contact. *Phone number of the contact.
Group This class creates object Group and contains all methods that deals with this object. Object Group represents a group of contacts. Object Group attributes : *User name : the user which this group of contacts belongs to. *Group name : name of the group. *Contact list : list of contacts at this group. *Path : path of the file *.txt that contains all the contacts.
Main This program represent a digital phone book , you can create groups of contacts , add, modify ,delete , search for contacts .
Method Containes all the static helping methods used in the project.
User This class creates object User and contains all methods that deals with this object. Object User represents a group of groups of contacts belongs to one person. Object User attributes : *User name : the user name which these groups of contacts belongs to. *Pass word : user's password to keep his privacy. *Path : path of the folder that contains the user groups.
